basicInfo.name: Victoria
basicInfo.flavor: Victoria took over her father's role as the Pirate King. She eventually solidified her position through her skills and strength.

Normal Attack.desc:
Single Enemy
 - Deals damage equal to 100% of Magic Attack 1 time(s).
スキル強化効果
 - Increases Damage: To 120% of Magic Attack.

Skill 1.name: Pistol Shot
Skill 1.desc:
Single Enemy
 - Deals damage equal to 285% of Magic Attack 1 time(s).
 - 100% chance to inflict Magic Vulnerability. [Duration: 5 Turn(s)]
スキル強化効果
 - Increases Damage: To 340% of Magic Attack.

Skill 2.name: Raise Morale
Skill 2.desc:
All Allies
 - Grants Magic Attack Boost. [Duration: 3 Turn(s)]
スキル強化効果
 - Increases Effect: Magic Attack Boost to 35%.
超越6段階達成効果
 - Increases Turns: Magic Attack Boost duration becomes. 4 turn(s).

Passive.name: Pirate Queen
Passive.desc:
Self
 - Heals HP equal to 90% of the caster's Magic Attack upon using a skill 1 time(s).
 - All Allies
 - Grants Paralysis Immunity. [Duration: 2 Turn(s)]
 - Grants Paralysis Immunity upon using a basic attack 1 time(s). [Duration: 2 Turn(s)]
スキル強化効果
 - Self
 - Adds Healing: Heals HP equal to 90% of Magic Attack upon activating a skill 1 time(s).
超越2段階達成効果
 - Back Row Allies
 - Adds Effect: 22% Physical Resistance. [Always Active]
